description: If you're looking for a random fact all you need do is ask and Alexa will return one from a list of almost 200. All you need is Alexa, no additional hardware required.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask random facts to tell me a random fact.
Alexa, ask random facts to give me a random fact.
Alexa, launch random facts and give me a fact.
name: Random Facts
shortDescription: Random Facts provides you with a random fact.
